        ],
        "props": [
          "assets/story/pixel-worlds-v1/props/forest/forest-12.webp"
        ]
      },
      "lines": [
        {
          "type": "narration",
          "text": "小小探险家来到雨滴工坊。让雨滴水车重新转动。，新的线索正在等着被发现。",
          "character": "narrator"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "这里就是雨滴工坊。我们先把“修好水车”记在地图上。",
          "character": "hero",
          "position": "left"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "我闻到了叶子和雨水的味道，森林朋友就在附近。",
          "character": "pet",
          "position": "right"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "先听树叶的声音，再用温柔的动作帮助这里的朋友。",
          "character": "forest_guide",
          "position": "left"
        },
        {
          "type": "activity",
          "activityType": "repair",
          "prompt": "让雨滴水车重新转动。",
          "character": "forest_guide",
          "position": "right",
          "actions": [
            {
              "label": "装回木齿轮",
              "feedback": "水车咕噜咕噜转起来。"
            },
            {
              "label": "清理小树枝",
              "feedback": "水流恢复，花田喝到了水。"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "narration",
          "text": "小小探险家完成了第一步，装回木齿轮让周围的线索变得清楚起来。",
          "character": "narrator"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "看！刚才藏起来的线索露出来了。",
          "character": "hero",
          "position": "left"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "轻轻完成这一步，藏在叶影里的小路出现了。",
          "character": "pet",
          "position": "right"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "把这条小路和森林地图连起来，萤光就会为我们领路。",
          "character": "forest_guide",
          "position": "left"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "记住这片叶子的形状，下一次遇见它就知道该往哪里走。",
          "character": "forest_guide",
          "position": "left"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "做完这一小步，回家的星图又亮了一格。我们继续出发吧！",
          "character": "pet",
          "position": "right"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "storyVersion": 2,
  "icon": "assets/story/pixel-worlds-v1/icons/forest/flower-compass.webp"
